# Playas Cantabria

Spanish-language monorepo: beach info app for Cantabria, Spain.
- `backend/` — Express + TypeScript, hexagonal architecture
- `frontend/` — Ionic React + Capacitor mobile/web app

## Conventions
- All code, comments, UI text in Spanish
- Backend: strict hexagonal layers, manual DI, never delete providers
- Frontend: Ionic components, co-located CSS, hooks only, mobile-first

## Skills
Read `.agents/skills/{name}/SKILL.md` when working on matching tasks:
- accessibility, frontend-design, vercel-composition-patterns, vercel-react-best-practices (frontend)
- nodejs-backend-patterns, nodejs-best-practices (backend)
- typescript-advanced-types (both)

See CLAUDE.md, frontend/CLAUDE.md, backend/CLAUDE.md for full docs.
